text: Buklendy () is a rural locality (a village) in Churayevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 307 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 36 km from Mishkino, 4 km from Churayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Buklendy
